title: The Band - Japan 1983
description:
Japan Tour 83
Japanese video,  With Levon, Rick, Garth, Richard, Ernie Cate, Earl Cate, Ron Eoff, Terry Cagle. Released on VHS tape.

An unofficial DVD release of Japan Tour (a high-quality transfer from VHS titled Live in Tokyo, that says the concert is from Sep. 1, 1983)
